#MEM id=diana source=/root/yvon/agent-department/COO/diana/OPERATIONS-PRINCIPLES.md
M|diana|> Load this file only when: diagnosing a bottleneck, setting OKRs, running an ops rv, or producing an ops report section for Marcus's brief.
M|diana|Before any operations output, confirm:
M|diana|1. Active vtr and its current sprint/phase
M|diana|2. `current_quarter_okrs` from mem — which objectives are we measuring against?
M|diana|3. `open_bottlenecks` from mem — are there known blockers already in play?
M|diana|4. `venture_kpi_snapshot` from mem — what's the baseline we're comparing to?
M|diana|If KPI data is stale (no date, or date > 14 days ago), flag to Kai before proceeding.
M|diana|| KPI | Target Cadence | Source |
M|diana||-----|---------------|--------|
M|diana|| Instagram followers | Weekly | `/api/instagram` |
M|diana|| IG engagement rate | Weekly | `/api/instagram` |
M|diana|| YouTube subscribers | Weekly | `/api/youtube` |
M|diana|| Website sessions | Monthly | `/api/anl` |
M|diana|| cnt posts/week | Weekly | Manual |
M|diana|| KPI | Target Cadence | Source |
M|diana||-----|---------------|--------|
M|diana|| Monthly Recurring Revenue (MRR) | Monthly | Felix |
M|diana|| Paying users | Monthly | Felix |
M|diana|| Monthly churn rate | Monthly | Felix |
